Oceanic Considering Offers From Three Investors, ThisDay Says

-- B y   E l i s h a   B a l a - G b o g b o
-- 
2011-07-01T09:06:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-01/oceanic-considering-offers-from-three-investors-thisday-says.html
Nigeria ’s  Oceanic Bank International
Plc (OCEANIC)  is considering offers from three potential bidders ahead of
the central bank’s Sept. 30 recapitalization deadline for
rescued lenders,  ThisDay  reported, citing Managing Director John Aboh.  The lender will make an official announcement within three
weeks, the Lagos-based newspaper said, cited Aboh, who didn’t
identify the bidders.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Elisha Bala-Gbogbo in Abuja at 
 ebalagbogbo@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Paul Richardson at 
 pmrichardson@bloomberg.net  